      "note": "Interjeição mantida."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18432e",
      "back_en": "Wh-What the hell are they saying...!?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x184385",
      "back_en": "a cold gaze at me, like I'm pure trash.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'lixo puro' equivale a 'utter scum'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1843dc",
      "back_en": "is getting the wrong idea here.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
